<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Chihowa holitopa ma! ƲIT56</title>
<time_sig>L.M. 8.8.8.8.</time_sig>
<aka>Ʋmmi fehna chia hoke;</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chihowa holitopa ma!
 Ʋmmi fehna chia hoke;
 Chi anukchieto li kʋt,
 Nana ishit sa yukpʋshke.

[V2]
 Nana inla yokak heno
 Naksika bohlit taiyahlit,
 Chishno ak bieka hona
 Chim antia sa bʋnnʋshke.

[V3]
 A̱ki pulla chia hokʋt,
 Ʋba ya̱ yakni achukma
 Nita̱ki bieka hona
 Is sʋm atahli tok oke.

[V4]
 Yʋmohmi pulla tok oka,
 Yakni i̱lʋppa issa likkmʋt,
 Ʋba nita̱ki yakni ma
 Ont chukowa la hi oke.

[V5]
 Yʋmma ona li hokmʋto
 Chihowa a binili ka,
 I̱ bili̱kasi fehna ka,
 Ont binili la hi oke.</lyrics>
<author>Alfred Wright</author>
<hymn_number>56</hymn_number>
</song>